::Zardus::

Zardus nods. "I see."

He looks the bot over. He wasn't fooled, but there was no use in 
questioning the bot further. "You'll need guest quarters at the 
Alliance base," he says. Astral comes up beside him.

"Me and my team are ready for duty, sir." The bot reports. Zardus 
nods.

"Excellent," the Alliance leader says, "Lead Cerebrus to some guest 
quarters. He needs a room and a tour of the base."

Astral nods, looking at Cerebrus. "I guess I'm gonna show ya around."
